{"tid":2340824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<聖誕文告> 英女王：即使在最黑暗的夜晚，新的黎明仍然充滿希望","createTime":"2020-12-25T21:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T01:42:02.000Z","uid":227801,"like":106,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"4847fbc8fe58ed1da3494e68fcddeab05b2b48bd","tid":2340824,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T21:01:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uSftQu9rnBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuSftQu9rnBA&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=35159912\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uSftQu9rnBA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/2C2Zb56lEK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F2C2Zb56lEK%2F&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=caf27289\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/2C2Zb56lEK/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567144-20201226.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567144-20201226.htm&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=cc25c43a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567144-20201226.htm&h=89145b89\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567144-20201226.htm</a><br />\n英女王伊利沙伯二世發表聖誕文告，向今年無朋友和家人陪伴的人保證，大家並不孤單。<br />\n<br />\n英女王在預錄的講話中提到，對很多人來說，今年充滿悲傷，有人失去至親，亦有人不能夠與親友見面，很多人只是想在聖誕節得到一個簡單的擁抱，但即使在最黑暗的夜晚，新的黎明亦有希望，雖然疫情造成困難，但同時令大家更親近，特別感謝前線人員及年輕人的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n受疫情影響，英女王今年只是與王夫菲臘親王留在溫莎堡過聖誕，未有好像往年一樣，與家人在桑德靈厄姆莊園聚會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201225/PTAXRTLYXRD4JDBSDWPGO5SGRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201225%2FPTAXRTLYXRD4JDBSDWPGO5SGRQ%2F&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=c65aac59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201225%2FPTAXRTLYXRD4JDBSDWPGO5SGRQ%2F&h=7849afa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201225/PTAXRTLYXRD4JDBSDWPGO5SGRQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n2020武漢肺炎蹂躪全球，很多人為了防疫，無法與親友聚首，英女皇伊利沙伯二世今年也無法一家共聚。今年聖誕文告一如以往預先錄影，但拍攝地點則改為溫莎堡，她在今年聖誕文告中談到疫情，坦言感受到國民今年聖誕因為武漢肺炎疫情，而與家人分開的痛苦及悲傷，但「生活必須繼續下去」。<br />\n<br />\n她向在疫情中失去親人或朋友的不幸者，或因為要保持安全社交距離而無法一家團聚人士致以慰問，「如果你是其中一員，你並不孤獨，讓我向你送上我的祝福」，又呼籲大家要抱有希望，「即使在最黑暗的時劇，新的黎明仍然充滿希望」。<br />\n<br />\n她又讚揚英國及全球醫護人員如何努力面對這個挑戰，指疫情雖然令大家要保持距離，但同時又更加親近，「大家努力迎接挑戰，我為這種不屈不撓的精神感到驕傲」，令她深受感動，讓大家明白在神的眼中，每個人都是特別、平等。<br />\n<br />\n今年聖誕女皇因疫情關係，無法如往年般到桑德靈厄姆大宅享受四代同堂天倫樂，只跟皇夫菲臘親王留在溫莎堡，其他皇室成員亦各自留在家中。<br />\n[ur"},{"pid":"e0062da87c8c662bd894479dcfd78256d922f361","tid":2340824,"uid":36383,"like":92,"dislike":1,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T21:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FPouY7C.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFPouY7C.gif&h=f16d76f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d32244e49248114159a7025364d6a2bc729b12d","tid":2340824,"uid":243380,"like":7,"dislike":143,"score":-136,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T21:16:00.000Z","msg":"老喇<br />\n早啲訓"},{"pid":"a95bd0b05a54c10617d888e9f4ad5eada524da6e","tid":2340824,"uid":55533,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T21:18:50.000Z","msg":"God Save the Queen<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5566a2a08aaf1424a276f479f7245ddf6b482cb4","tid":2340824,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T21:46:44.000Z","msg":"Until dawn,有命捱到日出先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0efde9a2d45493bbde73fb847c9589cc202bad2","tid":2340824,"uid":134683,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T21:49:10.000Z","msg":"Long live the Queen<br />